# Paramètres d'intégration Waldur ↔ OpenStack (copier en .env — GITIGNORÉ, contient des secrets).
# Servent à renseigner l'offre Marketplace OpenStack.Tenant (secret_options) + le SSO.

# --- OpenStack (application credential dédiée, PAS un mot de passe perso) ---
OS_BACKEND_URL=https://<keystone>:5000/v3
OS_APPLICATION_CREDENTIAL_ID=change-me
OS_APPLICATION_CREDENTIAL_SECRET=change-me
OS_ADMIN_TENANT_NAME=admin
OS_DOMAIN=Default
OS_EXTERNAL_NETWORK_ID=<uuid-reseau-externe-IP-flottantes>

# --- Waldur (admin bootstrap) ---
WALDUR_ADMIN_EMAIL=admin@polytechnique.edu
WALDUR_ADMIN_PASSWORD=change-me
WALDUR_PUBLIC_URL=https://waldur.<domaine>

# --- SSO (OIDC/Keycloak ↔ LDAP établissement) ---
OIDC_ISSUER=https://vm-pool-manager.mesocentre.plateau-de-saclay.net/dex
OIDC_CLIENT_ID=waldur
OIDC_CLIENT_SECRET=change-me
